text: Eunidia tripunctata is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Per Olof Christopher Aurivillius in 1911.BioLib.cz - Eunidia tripunctata. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==Subspecies== * Eunidia tripunctata nigricornis Breuning, 1950 * Eunidia tripunctata tripunctata Aurivillius, 1911 ==References== Category:Eunidiini Category:Beetles described in 1911
title: Eunidia tripunctata
